title: Time To Break Fedora 40 KDE 6!!
description:
KDE Plasma 6 is just around the corner and so is Fedora 40 which is planning to ship it but both are still in need of a lot of testing and right now it's the perfect time to do so, it's the Fedora 40 KDE test week and it's time to break some software
